<main class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 single-content-sidebar">


            <h1>Who are we</h1>

            <p>This a user group for programmers/developers. We meet monthly in Chester to listen to a talk from an industry expert, share experiences and eat pizza. We are not language specific.</p>

            <h2>How does it work</h2>
            <p>All our events are listed on <a href="https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/o/chester-devs-105644745611">Eventbrite</a>, <a href="https://discord.gg/xn7JfpXd">Discord</a> and <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/chester-devs/">LinkedIn</a>.</p>

            <h2>Topics</h2>
            <p>Our talks are quite varied in both in topic and in the experience level of the target audience. We have had talks on programming languages, architecture, project/team management, data stores, best practice, technology.</p>

            <h2>Speakers</h2>
            <p>Some of our speakers are Chester Dev members, or local experts, some come from quite a distance to to give talks they offer at conferences. Our speakers all give their time for free, although we occasionally help with travel costs. </p>

            <h2>Money</h2>
            <p>All our events are free to attendees. We cover costs via our Recruitment Panel, Sponsorship. For details see our <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Pages" asp-route-view="SponorshipDetail">Funding Details page</a>.</p>

        </div><!-- main-content/col -->
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-3 ml-auto single-content-sidebar-area">
            <partial name="_AboutSideNav"/>
        </div>
    </div>
</main> <!-- /container -->

